'''Henry Gardner''' is the son of [[Cassidy Gardner]].

==History==
Henry came into the ER with his mother, after she fell down the stairs. Henry had found her and called 911. Henry waited with Amelia while his mother got examined. They determined that his mother needed surgery, so he waited with a nurse while she was in surgery. After surgery, Henry got to see his mother, who promised to take him to the zoo when she was all better.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
He is being raised by a single mother. He was extremely worried about her when he found her on the basement floor.
